renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. params._rentPrices: The price array. Each element corresponds to a specific                    name length; names longer than the length of the array                    default to the price of the last element. Values are                    in tfuelWei per seconds.
